  <div class="grid-item-3 inner--l">
    <p class="fine-print">Challenge</p>
    <p>NHF needed expert help to present a plan, objectives and strategies with a high likelihood of reaching younger women.</p> 
    <p>NHF needed expertise in designing large-scale online, print and social networking campaigns that demonstrate results. </p>
    <p>A particularly difficult challenge is many women don't recognize heavy menstrual bleeding &mdash; a hallmark symptom of von Willebrand disease &mdash; as a problem. Therefore, NHF was tasked with raising awareness and offer ways to seek help.</p>
  </div>
