  <div class="grid-item-5 inner--l">
    <p class="fine-print">Solution</p>   
    <p>NHF's strong reputation and national programs served as the foundation for our work. We helped them tailor outreach with women and health providers, who evaluate symptoms.</p>
    <p>We researched examples of social marketing campaigns, which had strong evidence. And we adapted those strategies to reach measurable goals.</p> 
    <p>Next, we incorporated the strategies into proposal narrative, logic model and evaluation strategy. Due to the complexity of the project, we created tables that mapped each goal, strategy, measurement method and long-term outcome.</p> 
    <p>Finally, we worked with NHF to hone the logic to align with the CDC's priorities.</p>      
  </div>  
